name: DailyGoal
0:
”Alexa, open Daily Goal.”
”What is my goal for today?”
”What should I do today?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: daily goal
des: Alexa will tell you a task that you should complete for the day, and it is your duty to do whatever she asks of you. Tasks range from learning something new to doing some exercises; these are easy tasks to help improve your life one day at a time.
